songs.title: Song 2
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Woohoo!
Woohoo!
Woohoo!
Woohoo!

[Verse 1]
I got my head checked
By a jumbo jet
It wasn't easy
But nothing is, c'mon!

[Chorus]
(Woohoo!) When I hear heavy metal
(Woohoo!) And I'm pins and I'm needles
(Woohoo!) When, I'm comin' up easy
All of the time when I get that way, it ain't easy
But nothin' else is!
Woohoo!

[Verse 2]
I got my head done
When I was young
It's not my problem
It's not my problem

[Chorus]
(Woohoo!) When I hear heavy metal
(Woohoo!) And I'm pins and I'm needles
(Woohoo!) When, I'm comin' up easy
All of the time when I get that way-zay
But nothin' else is!

[Outro]
Woohoo!
(Now) woohoo!
Woohoo!
